<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h4>Hello <%= @name %>,</h4>
    <p>
      <b>You have a report for your area.</b> <br />
      Please check details below:
      <br />
      <p>
        <b>User Reporting:</b> <%= @report.user.username %><br />
        <b>Area:</b> <%= @report.intersection.area.name %><br />
        <b>Description:</b> <%=@report.description%><br />
        <% @report.location.each do |loc| -%>
          <b>Longitude/Latitude:</b> <%=loc%><br />
        <% end -%>
      </p>
    </p>
    <p>
      Log in to <%= @home_url %> and signoff on the area.<br />
      Contact us for any questions and queries.<br /> <br /><i>This email is auto generated by Bunjil, do not reply
      if you believe you have recieved this email by mistake, simply delete it.</i>
      <br/><br/>

      
      Regards,<br /> <i>The Bunjil Forest Watch Dev Team</i></p>
  </body>
</html>
